{"tid":1779930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（政府風向？）鄭承隆︰可邀監警會加入獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-12-12T04:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T07:17:01.000Z","uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":335,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"7f85300d0f86c7abca0103607a1eb5059c5ede96","tid":1779930,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"鄭承隆︰可邀監警會加入獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】監警會前委員鄭承隆在本台節目時事全方位表示，監警會國際專家組成員上月已提出監警會的權力不足，對小組成員退出不感驚訝，認為應加大監警會中部分委員會的權力。<br />\n<br />\n鄭承隆建議邀請監警會加入獨立調查委員會處理對警方的投訴，希望能減少警隊的抗拒，監警會的報告除交給行政長官，亦交給獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，監警會已成立十年需要改革，例如賦予主動調查的權力及委員組成更多元化。"},{"pid":"dcb345bdaa6e48fbebe96b5ac26bae9a7b89ee7c","tid":1779930,"uid":125168,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"呢班垃圾加入咗，仲算係獨立調查委員會？再講無真普選下嘅獨立調查都無太大意義"},{"pid":"f6be4aa82eb0d160a377b0059d0a0452810bc73c","tid":1779930,"uid":10125,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"叫人預埋你 咁 仲係唔係獨立<br />\n要人有邏輯係咪咁難"},{"pid":"93768a713f281ed3cdceee7cf2a175a6b95e57ac","tid":1779930,"uid":124277,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"林志偉出任獨立調查委員會主席"},{"pid":"6633045a5851e248098fc73363c22c5c8e09e2af","tid":1779930,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ecce30c0c1c51bca9c193667c28db0a1bff9bb95","tid":1779930,"uid":188176,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"唔可以比佢地加入啦<br />\n只可以作為其中一個比資料既組織<br />\n唔可以有權力但有責任比資料<br />\n用番佢地同一招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a77738e55c6f523fc9e5eac9c3ea1beec2bdde","tid":1779930,"uid":128417,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"俾佢哋加入咪即係又係自己人查自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc7984d244a70995269d7d8087016f2abe466a1","tid":1779930,"uid":237425,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"人地獨立調查委員會係法官主持架wo<br />\n你估阿豬阿狗都做得架?<br />\n<br />\n<em>一般來説，調查委員會的主席職務由榮休法官擔綱；調查委員會僅接受來自行政長官連同行政會議的指示。委員會有權檢視各類證據、有關機構的文件檔案；強力傳召證人參與聆訊。根據以上授權，委員會的調查程序系一司法程序，因此有關抵觸委員會調查的行爲，會被視藐視罪，由委員會進行懲處。</em>"},{"pid":"f9ad9f49b2780586b4810204c0f5b40b1d13f7c7","tid":1779930,"uid":149973,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"而家香港法官仲信得過？<br />\n應該加入國際法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d1c1458edaa023d46fd8bf83325bf10c596a5c","tid":1779930,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"政府根本又想誤導大眾"},{"pid":"746703be23c9dfb86adbe5b0a80f4640b05d21e0","tid":1779930,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"鄭承隆建議邀請監警會加入獨立調查委員會處理對警方的投訴，希望能減少警隊的抗拒<br />\n<br />\n查狗仲要減少狗嘅抗拒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd33f9bd95992752c6304157ea198fea3895d50","tid":1779930,"uid":259813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:27:11.000Z","msg":"使乜理警甴抗唔抗拒，邊個查佢佢都抗拒架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6b4429b4a81a38946a052ce6195afd6e2caf76","tid":1779930,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ed84472244bd573a5d597c552398d6b297507d","tid":1779930,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5020caf22f60bb58c4ff1e1da929cfbebe6aa3","tid":1779930,"uid":306434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:28:11.000Z","m